						<p>Event Ticket Price : ${eventDetailsData[3]} Wei</p>
						<p>Total Tickets : ${eventDetailsData[4]} </p>
						<p>Available Tickets : ${eventDetailsData[5]} </p>
						<p>Sale Status : ${SaleStatusFormatter(eventDetailsData[6])} </p>
